Module guigame

Package guigame.gui.main

Contains all major classes for the GUI. Mostly windows / frames as well as the GUIGameBoard class.
  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    GUIGameBoard
    A GUIPanel containing the whole GameBoard.
    GUIGameBoardWindow
    Window for the GUIGameBoard.
    GUIGameOverWindow
    Implementation of JFrame: a Frame which is shown when the game is over.
    GUIGameWindow
    Frame to show the GUIMainMenu.
    GUIPauseMenuWindow
    Window to show a GUIPauseMenu.
